           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"answer-container solv-details">
                   =20
                    <button class=3D"btn reveal-solution-btn">Reveal the an=
swer</button>
                </div>
           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"question-container">
   =20
        <p>\[n^3 - 3n +7 \equiv 0 \pmod{n-5} \\
2n^2 - n +2 \equiv 0 \pmod{n+6}\]</p>

<p>What integer \( n \geq 5 \) satisfies the above system of congruence equ=
ations?</p>

   =20
</div>
           =20

            <div class=3D"solution-container hide">
                <br><br>
                The correct answer is: <strong>14</strong>
               =20
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<p></p>

<p></p><div class=3D"problem-modal-container anchor" id=3D"problem-my-calcu=
lator-isnt-good-enough">

