swer</button>
                </div>
           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"question-container">
   =20
        <p>\[ 1 \times 10^{1}+2 \times 10^{2}+3\times 10^{3}+\cdots+2015 \t=
imes 10^{2015}\]</p>

<p>What is the remainder when the number above is divided by 11?</p>

   =20
</div>
           =20

            <div class=3D"solution-container hide">
                <br><br>
                The correct answer is: <strong>4</strong>
               =20
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<p></p>

<p></p><div class=3D"problem-modal-container anchor" id=3D"problem-ukmt-int=
ermediate-challenge-iv">

