Answer" data-controller-inited=3D"true">

        <div class=3D"problem-container">
           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"answer-container solv-details">
                   =20
                    <button class=3D"btn reveal-solution-btn">Reveal the an=
swer</button>
                </div>
           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"question-container">
   =20
        <p>Bogdan divides 2015 successively by 1, 2, 3, ..., all the way up=
 to include 1000. He writes down the remainder for each division. What is t=
he largest remainder he writes down?</p>

   =20
</div>
           =20

            <div class=3D"solution-container hide">
                <br><br>
                The correct answer is: <strong>671</strong>
               =20
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
