           =20

           =20
                <div class=3D"question-container">
   =20
        <p>\[\begin{align}
\begin{cases} x^2 + 3x - 7 &amp;\equiv 0 \pmod{71} \\=20
x^2 - 5x - 16 &amp;\equiv 0 \pmod{89}
\end{cases}
\end{align} \]</p>

<p>Let \(x\) be a positive integer satisfying the system of equations above=
. What is the least possible value of \(x?\)</p>

   =20
</div>
